[SN]TITLE[SN]
Balloon show nearly gets blown away

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Strong winds caused chaos at a hot air balloon festival in Wisconsin, in America.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
20 July 2015 Last updated at 12:35 BST
Staff struggled to control one balloon which landed on its side while another was whipped up in the air before crashing back down towards the crowd.
Fortunately no one was hurt.
